\nhydrogen-rich crystals, a direct detection experiment can be built for\nmeasuring the large unexplored parameter space of light DM particles.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Jan 2022 22:34:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 10 Mar 2022 16:43:02 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 20 Sep 2022 22:41:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-22"}
