ull multiplet structure\ndue to intra-atomic and crystal field interactions in Oh and D3d symmetry,\nclearly reproduced the dichroic trend in experimental RIXS spectra.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 Jan 2022 10:35:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-13"}
