 {\\it in situ} accretion,\nare highlighted. Moreover, jelly-fish morphologies appear as these galaxies\nachieve their maximum star formation rate, before their quenching phase.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Jan 2022 17:45:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-14"}
